{"lemma":"سِقايَةُ","slug":"سِقايَةُ","root":"س.ق.#","root_slug":"س-ق-_","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ق-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سِقايَة","root":"سقي","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20146","n20147"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%90%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%8A%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20146","headword_ar":"سُقَايَةٌ","root":"sqY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n20147","headword_ar":"سِقَايَةٌ","root":"sqY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suqaAyapN","text_ar":"سُقَايَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqaApN","text_ar":"مَسْقَاةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoqaApN","text_ar":"مِسْقَاةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place for giving to drink"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for watering:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaAyapu AlmaA='i","text_ar":"سِقَايَةُ المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is well known: (S:) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaAyapN","text_ar":"سِقَايَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, for the giving to drink to people:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a construction for water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which beverage is made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, at the fairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"festivals, &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, T, TA:) [and particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which a beverage made of raisins steeped in water was given at the general assembly of the pilgrims:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqaApN","text_ar":"مَسْقَاةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a drinkingplace"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in a general sense]: and he who pronounces it with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"[↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoqaApN","text_ar":"مِسْقَاةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] makes it to be like the utensil called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoqaApu Ald~iyki","text_ar":"مِسْقَاةُ الدِّيكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the drinking-vessel of the cock"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turofapN","text_ar":"تُرْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masaAqK","text_ar":"مَسَاقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaAyapN","text_ar":"سِقَايَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vessel in which one is given to drink:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) in the Kur [xii. 70], it means the king's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drinking-cup;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuwaAE","text_ar":"صُوَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which he drank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and with which they measured corn; and it was a vessel of silver."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaAyapu AlHaAji","text_ar":"سِقَايَةُ الحَاجِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beverage made of raisins steeped in water which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tribe of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Kureysh used to give to the pilgrims to drink:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it was under the superintendence of El-'Abbás in the Time of Ignorance and in El-Islám: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaAyap","text_ar":"سِقَايَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this phrase is an inf. n.; so in the Kur ix. 19; (Mgh;) where it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajaEalotumo","text_ar":"اَجَعَلْتُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaAyapa A@loHaAji waEimaArapaA@lomasojidi A@loHaraAmi kamano A=mana biA=ll~`hi","text_ar":"سِقَايَةَ ا@لْحَاجِ وَعِمَارَةَا@لْمَسْجِدِ ا@لْحَرَامِ كَمَنْ ا=مَنَ بِا=للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@lyawomi A@loA=xiri","text_ar":"وَا@ليَوْمِ ا@لْا=خِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the two words"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sqAyp","text_ar":"سقاية"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EmArp","text_ar":"عمارة"},{"kind":"text","text":"being inf. ns. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaY","text_ar":"سَقَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamara","text_ar":"عَمَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Bd;) the meaning being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajaEalotumo A^ahola siqaAyapi AlHaAji wa EimaArapi Almasojidi AlHaraAmi","text_ar":"اَجَعَلْتُمْ اَهْلَ سِقَايَةِ الحَاجِ وَ عِمَارَةِ المَسْجِدِ الحَرَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Have ye made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pronounced, the authors of the giving to drink to the pilgrims, and of the keeping in repair of the sacred mosque, to be like him who has believed in God and the last day?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and this is confirmed by another reading, which is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suqaApa AlHaAji waEamarapa Almasojidi","text_ar":"سُقَاةَ الحَاجِ وَعَمَرَةَ المَسْجِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ksh, Bd:) or the meaning is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajaEalotumo siqaAyapa AlHaAji kaA_iymaAni mano A=mana","text_ar":"اَجَعَلْتُمْ سِقَايَةَ الحَاجِ كَاـِيمَانِ مَنْ ا=مَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c., i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have ye made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pronounced, the giving to drink to the pilgrims,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be like the belief of him who has believed"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.?]. (Bd.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rifaAdapN","text_ar":"رِفَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","Mgh","JK","T","TA","K","Ksh","Bd"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}